text: Alena Polozkova is a retired gymnast from Belarus. Polozkova competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. She was born on 11 August 1979.Alena Polozkova == References == Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian gymnasts Category:Olympians for Belarus
